{"tid":1712981,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"拔萃男書院3名中六生昨涉非法集結被捕　今獲准保釋","createTime":"2019-11-12T15:59:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T16:00:45.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bfe5b0d29510704a54fc9efbc532ed004f8a3977","tid":1712981,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T15:59:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3542803/org/a4abea44ab140a1e5ac0ad004a12b464.jpg/ZUZXtz2aC9rryEx4h6Th6JxnHNifdWVRwMfIdOrHyHQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3542803%2Forg%2Fa4abea44ab140a1e5ac0ad004a12b464.jpg%2FZUZXtz2aC9rryEx4h6Th6JxnHNifdWVRwMfIdOrHyHQ&h=6782b96e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n英華書院一名中二學生昨晨在校門外播放《願榮光歸香港》，被警方以涉嫌「在公眾地方行為不檢」拘捕。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n有網民連續兩日早上發動罷工及堵塞交通的行動。《香港01》獲悉，有三名拔萃男書院學生昨日於旺角一帶被警方以非法集結拘捕，今（12日）已獲准保釋外出。據了解，三位男生為修讀國際預科文憑（IB）第12班的學生，其中一人更是校內成績優異生。《香港01》正向校方及警方查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>英華中二男生昨早校門播《榮光》被捕</strong><br />\n<br />\n另外，英華書院昨日早上，有一名14歲中二學生在校門對出以藍牙播放器播放《願榮光歸香港》，被警方拘捕。警方表示，警員於昨晨約7時50分巡經長沙灣東京街西與深旺道交界期間，發現一名男童在現場以擴音器播放歌曲，引致多人到場聚集，以涉嫌「在公眾地方行為不檢」拘捕該名男童，已獲准保釋候查，下月中旬須向警方報到。案件由深水埗警區刑事調查隊第三隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n據該校反修例關注組昨日指，當時該男生並沒有作出任何堵路或違法的行為，並發聲明譴責警方無理拘捕，並呼籲學校正視事件的嚴重性，給予被捕學生適切的支援。《香港01》已向校方查詢，正待回覆。<br />\n<br />\n撰文：胡家欣　鄺曉斌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/397356/11-11%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E6%8B%94%E8%90%83%E7%94%B7%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A23%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%98%A8%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E4%BB%8A%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F397356%2F11-11%25E4%25B8%2589%25E7%25BD%25B7-%25E6%258B%2594%25E8%2590%2583%25E7%2594%25B7%25E6%259B%25B8%25E9%2599%25A23%25E5%2590%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2585%25AD%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%2598%25A8%25E6%25B6%2589%25E9%259D%259E%25E6%25B3%2595%25E9%259B%2586%25E7%25B5%2590%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595-%25E4%25BB%258A%25E7%258D%25B2%25E5%2587%2586%25E4%25BF%259D%25E9%2587%258B&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7fDXWQKahOldmH8%2Bpia8yKE%3D&h=a3fc366b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/397356/11-11%E4%B8%89%E7%BD%B7-%E6%8B%94%E8%90%83%E7%94%B7%E6%9B%B8%E9%99%A23%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%85%AD%E7%94%9F%E6%98%A8%E6%B6%89%E9%9D%9E%E6%B3%95%E9%9B%86%E7%B5%90%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95-%E4%BB%8A%E7%8D%B2%E5%87%86%E4%BF%9D%E9%87%8B</a>"},{"pid":"c949aa7335f8127a62b5b27dcee9d4abf420ecf5","tid":1712981,"uid":60831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:00:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50ff470d18267f3567ce9d4e954676ec3ee62214","tid":1712981,"uid":36238,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T16:00:45.000Z","msg":"條罪就嚟等同莫須有"}]}